## Solution

Implemented `findAnagrams` in `anagram.js`:

```js
export const findAnagrams = (subject, candidates) => {
  const sorted = (word) => word.toLowerCase().split('').sort().join('');
  const subjectLower = subject.toLowerCase();
  const subjectSorted = sorted(subject);
  return candidates.filter((candidate) => {
    const candidateLower = candidate.toLowerCase();
    return candidateLower !== subjectLower && sorted(candidate) === subjectSorted;
  });
};
```

**Key logic:**
- Sort letters of each word (case-insensitively) to compare anagrams
- Exclude the subject word itself (case-insensitive comparison)
- Return candidates whose sorted letters match the subject's sorted letters

